---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import InfoSection from '../../components/InfoSection.astro';
import { SITE } from '../../data/site';

const lang = 'en';

const title = 'Privacy Policy - Goose Goose Duck Guide';
const description =
  'Goose Goose Duck Guide Privacy Policy: how we use Google AdSense (including third-party cookies and how to opt out of personalized ads), Cloudflare Web Analytics anonymous traffic stats, and how we handle messages sent via the contact form.';

const updated = '2026-06-16';

const jsonLd = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@graph': [
    { '@type': 'Article', headline: title, description, inLanguage: 'en' },
    {
      '@type': 'BreadcrumbList',
      itemListElement: [
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 1, name: 'Home', item: new URL('/en/', Astro.site).href },
        { '@type': 'ListItem', position: 2, name: 'Privacy Policy' },
      ],
    },
  ],
};
---
<Base title={title} description={description} jsonLd={jsonLd} lang={lang}>
  <div class="wrap detail">
    <div class="crumb"><a href="/en/">Home</a> / Privacy Policy</div>
    <h1>Privacy<span class="em"> Policy</span></h1>
    <p class="lead">This policy explains what information {SITE.name} ({Astro.site?.host}) comes into contact with when you visit the site, who processes it, for what purpose, and how you can control it. Last updated: {updated}.</p>

    <div class="detail-layout-single">
      <main>
        <section class="sec">
          <h2>📌 One-Sentence Summary</h2>
          <p>This is a free player-made strategy resource site for <em>Goose Goose Duck</em>. <strong>We do not actively collect personally identifiable information</strong> (such as real name or phone number) and we do not require registration or login. Traffic statistics use an anonymous, cookie-free method. Advertising is served via Google AdSense, which may use cookies. Details below.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="sec">
          <h2>🍪 Advertising & Cookies (Google AdSense)</h2>
          <p>We use <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to display ads that help keep the site running. What you should know about ad cookies:</p>
          <ul class="kv">
            <li>As a third-party ad provider, <strong>Google and its partners use cookies and similar device identifiers</strong> to serve ads based on your past visits to this and other sites.</li>
            <li>Google uses advertising cookies to enable itself and its partners to deliver <strong>personalized ads</strong> based on your browsing behavior.</li>
            <li>This site itself does not read or store these advertising cookies and cannot access the data Google collects through them. Processing of this data is governed by <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/ads" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Google’s advertising policies</a>.</li>
          </ul>
          <p><strong>How to turn off personalized ads:</strong> Visit <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Google Ads Settings</a> or go to <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">www.aboutads.info</a> to opt out of personalized ads from third-party vendors. You will still see ads, but they will be less relevant to you.</p>
          <p class="hint">Note: All ads on this site are automatically served by Google. We have no control over which specific ads are shown.</p>
        </section>

        <InfoSection title="Traffic Statistics (Cloudflare Web Analytics)" icon="📊">
          <p>We use <strong>Cloudflare Web Analytics</strong> for anonymous traffic measurement to understand overall visit volume and popular pages so we can improve content. What you should know:</p>
          <ul class="kv">
            <li>Cloudflare Web Analytics <strong>does not use cookies</strong> and <strong>does not store or read any identifiers on your device</strong>.</li>
            <li>It <strong>does not collect any information that can identify you personally</strong> and does not track your browsing behavior across sites.</li>
            <li>It only collects aggregated anonymous metrics such as page views, referrers, and device types. See <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Cloudflare Web Analytics</a> and its privacy documentation for details.</li>
          </ul>
        </InfoSection>

        <InfoSection title="Contact Messages" icon="📨">
          <p>The site has no registration, login, or commenting features and <strong>will not proactively ask you for any personal information</strong>.</p>
          <p>If you voluntarily email us using the address on the <a href="/en/contact/">Contact page</a>, the email address and message content <strong>will only be used to reply to your message</strong>. It will not be used for mass marketing and will not be sold or shared with third parties. Once we have handled your request we are not obligated to retain the correspondence.</p>
        </InfoSection>

        <InfoSection title="Third-Party Links" icon="🔗">
          <p>Some pages link to external sites (game wikis, community sources, etc.). Those sites have their own independent privacy policies. This policy does not cover their practices; please review the relevant site’s terms when you visit them.</p>
        </InfoSection>

        <InfoSection title="Minors" icon="👶">
          <p>The site provides general game strategy content and is not designed for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
        </InfoSection>

        <InfoSection title="Policy Updates" icon="🔄">
          <p>This policy may be updated as our services change. The “Last updated” date at the top of this page will be revised. For significant changes we will try to post a clear notice on the site. Continued use of the site after an update means you understand and accept the current version of this policy.</p>
        </InfoSection>

        <InfoSection title="Questions?" icon="📮" variant="compact">
          <p>If you have any questions about this privacy policy, please reach out via the <a href="/en/contact/">Contact page</a>. You may also want to read <a href="/en/about/">About the Site</a>.</p>
        </InfoSection>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .detail{padding-top:24px}
  h1{font-size:38px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-top:6px}
  h1 .em{background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--goose),var(--neutral) 50%,var(--duck));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
  .lead{color:var(--txt-dim);font-size:16.5px;margin:14px 0 18px;max-width:760px}
  .detail-layout-single{max-width:820px;margin-bottom:40px}
  .sec a{color:var(--accent)}
  .sec strong{color:var(--txt)}
  .hint{font-size:13px;color:var(--txt-dim)!important}
  .kv{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:9px;margin:4px 0 12px}
  .kv li{font-size:15px;color:var(--txt-dim);line-height:1.65;padding-left:18px;position:relative}
  .kv li::before{content:'›';position:absolute;left:0;top:-1px;color:var(--accent);font-weight:700}
  .kv li strong{color:var(--txt)}
  .next p{color:var(--txt-dim)}
  @media(max-width:920px){h1{font-size:28px}}
</style>
